Vahaflix Privacy Policy
Vahaflix offers a variety of measures to protect your privacy when you use Vahaflix Services, includingVahaflix Sites, Vahaflix Software, and/or other Vahaflix Services, etc. Vahaflix has created this Data Privacy Policy ("Policy") which elaborates upon our privacy practices in order to make our users understand that how Personal Data of users "information" is collected, used, transferred through our websites and mobile applications ("Platform") and Users rights to their information who browse or access the Platform or provide any information to the Platform in regards to its services.

Any references in this Policy to "Vahaflix", "Company", "we", "our", "us" etc. will be interpreted as a reference to Vahaflix and any reference to as "Users", "You" or "Yours" is reference to user/ player of this app/ Platform. Whether you are new to Vahaflix or a long-time user, please do take the time to get to know our practices, and if you have any questions please feel free to contact us.

1. Information We Collect
Personal Information refers to any information about a living individual who can be identified from that information, either by itself or when it is combined with other information. However, in the course of the end userâ€™s interaction with the Services, we collect the following information:

Information you submit to us.You give us your information by registering your account, accessing website, availing our products and Services. This will also include information you provide to us by corresponding with us. This may also include your social media information and activity, based on your interaction with us. The following is a list of information collected from you when you register a community account:

