b. Mobile number: for the purposes of registration and creation of an account, correspondence with you;
c. Birth Date: for the purposes of verification of your age;
d. Gender: for the purposes of creating a profile;
e. Financial Information: for in-app purchases;
f. Personal Webpage â€“ where you intend to link your social media handles / profiles with us.

Information we collect automatically:

