Information we collect from third parties:
We may work with a limited number of third parties (including mobile network providers, and delivery service providers, collection agencies, analytics providers) to provide the Services and may receive information about you from such third parties. We also receive profile information from the social media platform/s that you use to log in or create accounts with us, as per their terms and policies.

We do not collect any further information from you, if not specifically mentioned hereinabove.

2. Why We Collect Information
We collect information (including Personal Information) to provide the Services and for the purposes as outlined below:
to help us identify you when you log into the Platform and when you register an account with us;

to help facilitate in-app purchases and make subscribed and paid content available to you;
to enhance the quality of the video services that we provide and to improve the effectiveness to better tailor our services to your interests and needs;
to validate, authorize and map a specific profile with an authorized user;
to the performance of a contractual obligation;
to communicate with you;
to provide you with news, special offers, and general information about other products and services;
to provide and process service requests initiated by you.
3. Disclosure and Sharing of Information
We may share the Personal Information (and other information) with third parties who provide us with infrastructure support services,including but not limited to our own affiliates affiliate platforms for the purposes of publication and hosting of content,for meeting the obligations agreed to between you and us.

We will never display, rent or sell your personally identifiable information to others.

We may also disclose your Personal Information:

As required by law, such as to comply with a judicial order, executive orders, requirement by a law enforcement authority, or by other legal processes;
When your desired products and services can only be provided if your personal information is disclosed;
When we are required to provide information to the companies that provide products or services on our behalf; (unless we notify you otherwise, these companies do not have the right to use your personally identifiable information);
When we believe in good faith that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, protect your safety or the safety of others, or, investigate fraud or crime;
If we (or our affiliates) are involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or substantially all of its assets or equity.
3.2 Information Access and Accuracy

It is your choice whether to send your personal information to us. When you provide information to us, you agree to provide accurate information only and agree that we may assume its accuracy and rely on it. Yet in some cases, if the information provided is incomplete or inaccurate we may not be able to offer Services accordingly.

4. Account Deletion Agreement
How to Delete Your Vahaflix Account?

You may delete your account through [Me â€“ Settings â€“ DeleteAccount]. We will process it for you as soon as possible within 7days after receiving your cancellation application and verifying your identity. After your account is deleted, your personal information will be removed from the Vahaflix App, except for the personal information that we must retain as explicitly required by laws.

For connecting, user disabling, or logging out from your Facebook (Meta)/Google connect credentials to us, all of your profile content and other information may be deleted upon deletion request. Vahaflix will log out the user from all their user accounts on Vahaflix and reset all user data. We will also disassociate your username, password, and all related information files and user content associated with or inside your account (or any part thereof), including your user content.

However, certain details are maintained with us for archival and legal purposes. Vahaflix will not have any liability whatsoever to you for any termination, suspension, or deletion of your user content. Vahaflix will hold and use the content/data as long as required and permissible under local laws. All provisions of the Agreement which should survive shall, including without limitation, warranty disclaimers, governing law, and limitations of liability.

4.1 What happens if I delete my Vahaflix account?

You won't be able to reactivate or use your Vahaflix account.Your profile, photos, videos, messages, comments, likes, shares,levels, followers, privileges, and digital contents (tickets / bonus) will be permanently deleted and can't be retrieved.

4.2 Who may initiate a request to delete my Vahaflix account?

In order to initiate a request to delete your Vahaflix account, you will need to meet all of the following requirements:
Your account is under normal operation. We can't handle requests for accounts that are hacked or compromised or involve fraudulent or illegal activities.
There are no large amounts of unconsumed or unwithdrawn assets in the account; large virtual assets such as tickets and bonus must be consumed or withdrawn first.
You are not a self-media producer or a content creator engaging in a separate agreement with us.
You are free from complaints, controversies, or disputes with us or any other third party because of your use of Vahaflix Services.
4.3 Can I cancel my account deletion?

You can cancel your account deletion if it is within 7 days since you initiated the deletion request. After 7 days, your account and all your information will be permanently deleted, and you won't be able to retrieve your information.

Additional Information:

During our handling of your deletion request, we have the right to suspend your request without obtaining your permission if your account is reported or investigated by any other users or governmental body, or is otherwise related to any legal proceeding.
Requesting to delete your Vahaflix account will not free you from any obligation or duty, regardless of monetary or not, arising from your previous use of Vahaflix Services.
You should back up any information you would like to keep; otherwise, you may not be able to re-access the information in your Vahaflix account after it is deleted.
Your information may remain after your account is deleted in backup storage that we use to recover in the event of a disaster, software error, or other data loss event. We may also keep your information for things like legal issues, terms violations, or harm prevention efforts.
Please ensure that you've reviewed the document for consistency and legal compliance, especially with data protection laws and user agreements specific to your service.

